\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實佢哋用黎用去都係garam masala，薑黃粉，孜然粉，芫荽籽呢幾樣。落唔同肉，唔同「底」（蕃茄蓉／椰漿／其他nut milk），就已經可以演變成幾廿款唔同咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f42a8460a733368acc00b393e9f0018069aa5ed","tid":2404622,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:39:50.000Z","msg":"樓豬白卡佬黎<br />\n167一名<br />\n大家唔好鬧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54238b86f298570b29e4d6bf5c6439cbbd475ec","tid":2404622,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"得罪問句，樓豬你想點樣死法？死嘅方法過百種，點樣冚家剷又死得唔痛苦又係有難度"}]}